name: 30.WAD
description: My original goal was to try to draw out a level all in 1 sitting, then do all the sectors at once, ect. It turned out to have a kind of great uniformity to it...as you can see, unlike most of my earlier work the level kind of looks like a circle instead of a straight line...it's spread out. Look for the few glitches in the walls, as if you walk through them during deathmatch, it's a great place to hide. It looks really cool to see the other player leap out of the wall, BFG in hand...
